description: An illustration of a simple houseboat consisting of a single-room structure with a door, two windows on each side of the door, another window on the structure's left side, and a roof that extends past the structure's front wall to create an overhang which is supported by two blue poles. The platform upon which the house sits is various shades of blueish-green. There are several thin blue triangles below the houseboat representing waves in the water.
